The Aim of this assignment is to inspect and learn your coding practices as well as proficiency in
Django and DRF(Django Rest Framework).
1. Make a website using Django/DRF which allows a user to
○ Select a resume template from few options
○ Enter his/her details in a form, the fields can be:
○ Academic Details
○ Personal Details
○ Job Experience Details( Prev and Current)
○ Skills
Etc.
2. Submit the above form to download his Resume as a PDF and send the pdf to his email
too.
3. Please note, when the user submits the above form, all the form data must be stored in
SQLite database.